Human Resources Executive Trainee (HRET)
Responsibilities
You are a FRESH graduate or have 1 – 2 years’ experiences in Human Resources areaYou hold minimum Bachelor degree from a well-recognized Indonesian or International University majoring in Human Resources Management, Management, Psychology, Business Administration, or other related subjectsYou have a good command of written and spoken EnglishExcellent administration skill, details orientation, neat and order, and very organized individualYou have a strong passion in people and human resourcesSound logic and good with numbersYou are a person with sharp analyzing skills, high conceptual thinking, and ability to identify patterns or connections between situations that are not obviously relatedYou are computer literate (advanced Ms. Excel, Ms. Word, Ms. PowerPoint, and experiences in HR system would be an added value).You are energetic and easy-going person, especially love to learn and understand all HR functions and processesTHIS IS A GREAT OPPORTUNITY FOR YOU!  Please submit your application letter and CV, written in English.  You may also enclose your professional qualifications obtained with not more than 200 kb attachment, by writing in the subject Human Resources Executive Trainee (HRET), and send e-mail to:pc.indonesia@tnsglobal.com or Yogi.Atlin@tnsglobal.com “Only short-listed candidates will be invited via e-mail/phone for Test and Interview”
